General.Name: Clas Ohlson AB ser. B
General.Description: Clas Ohlson AB (publ) operates as a retail company in Sweden and internationally. It offers hardware, electrical, multimedia, home, and leisure products, as well as spare parts and accessories. The company sells its products through its stores, as well as online. Clas Ohlson AB (publ) was founded in 1918 and is headquartered in Insjön, Sweden.
